            Traditionally, business
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">journalists</ENAMEX> describe every increase in the overall trade deficit as a
"worsening." According to that tradition, I had a very bad day <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">yesterday</TIMEX>. But
it didn't feel like <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a bad day</TIMEX>--I like my new rug, and it would
have been inconvenient to put off buying it until <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a day</TIMEX> when I felt like
