how much you ought to care about what goes on in other <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">households</ENAMEX>.
Even if you are convinced that the average <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> spends too much, or earns
too little, or spends too little, or earns too much, it's not entirely clear
